caption: Foo Type + Editor Demo

This demo plugin registers a new content type `application/x-foo` and provides a simple custom editor widget `edit-foo`.

- Register type: in a startup module, we call `$tw.utils.registerFileType("application/x-foo","utf8",".foo",{deserializerType:"text/plain"})`.
- Map editor: we set `$:/config/EditorTypeMappings/application/x-foo` to `foo`, so the `<$edit>` meta-widget uses `<$edit-foo>` for tiddlers of this type.
